{#
/**
 * @file
 * Theme override to display a region.
 *
 * Available variables:
 * - content: The content for this region, typically blocks.
 * - attributes: HTML attributes for the region <div>.
 * - region: The name of the region variable as defined in the theme's
 *   .info.yml file.
 *
 * @see template_preprocess_region()
 */
#}
{%
  set classes = [
    'footer-top',
    'region',
    'region-' ~ region|clean_class,
  ]
%}
{% if content %}
  <div{{ attributes.addClass(classes) }}>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-3 pl-sm-3 pl-lg-3">
          <div class="cebu_title pt-5 px-3 pr-lg-0">
            <h3>Drupal in Cebu</h3>
            <p>This camp is brought to you by <a href="https://wwww.facebook.com/groups/drupalcebu" target="_blank">Drupal Cebu User Group</a></p>
            <p>Access the source code of this website on Github. This website is all open source</p>
            <p>Drupal meetups every last Wednesday of the month, find us on <a href="https://www.meetup.com/drupal-ph/" target="_blank">meetup.com</a></p>
            <p class="button-link">
              <a class="button-link text-display-large" href="https://www.meetup.com/drupal-ph/" target="_blank">Drupal Monthly Meetup
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="twitter_title pb-4 px-3 pl-lg-0">
            <h3>Drupal on Twitter</h3>
            <p> <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i><a href="https://twitter.com/DrupalCampCebu" target="_blank">@DrupalCampCebu.</a> Who said conferences are not funny? More photos from our last Drupalcamp Cebu: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.723538837835150&type=3" target="_blank">Official photos from last year's Drupalcamp Cebu 2017</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drupalcampcebu?src=hash" target="_blank"> #drupalcampcebu</a></p>
            <p> <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i><a href="https://twitter.com/DrupalCampCebu" target="_blank">@DrupalCampCebu.</a> Drupalcamp Cebu 2017 group photo. This was our largest Drupalcamp :) <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drupalcampcebu?src=hash" target="_blank">#drupalcampcebu</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drupalcamp?src=hash" target="_blank">#drupalcamp</a></p>
            <p> <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i><a href="https://twitter.com/DrupalCampCebu" target="_blank">@DrupalCampCebu.</a> Drupalcamp trainer <a href=" https://twitter.com/CasisMary" target="_blank">@CasisMary</a> published her full report from the event. Very interesting read with testimonials from attendees! Thanks Mary! <a href="https://www.prometsource.com/blog/drupalcamp-cebu-2017-review" target="_blank">prometsource.com/blog/drupalcamp-cebu-2017-review</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drupalcamp?src=hash" target="_blank">#drupalcamp</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drupalcampcebu?src=hash" target="_blank">#drupalcampcebu</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-6 px-0">
          <div class="col-12 px-0">
            <div class="map px-0">
              <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3925.597639108888!2d123.87922241442327!3d10.293967427854406!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x33a99c015a4bf233%3A0x95d783198f4634f8!2sCebu+Institute+of+Technology+-+University!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sph!4v1521721132774" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endif %}
